{"type":"message","id":"c3c0f857","parentId":"dca631ea","timestamp":"2026-03-24T09:38:22.793Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"我把这两件一起做：先修 `jimeng-auto-generator` 的结构/识别问题，再批量检查这些新 skills 缺哪些依赖，最后给你一个能不能直接用的结果。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_070d3cbb0915198e0169c25b8aeab081918865a5f3d5dd4f48\",\"phase\":\"commentary\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_PFBZI6Gmo5npZSnpApa1EljP|fc_070d3cbb0915198e0169c25b8ea080819190c0037e7e4dbf5a","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/Users/palpet/.openclaw/workspace/skills/jimeng-auto-generator/SKILL.md"},"partialJson":"{\"file_path\":\"/Users/palpet/.openclaw/workspace/skills/jimeng-auto-generator/SKILL.md\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_AsnqL37C9LM3SNFfyObcY2DE|fc_070d3cbb0915198e0169c25b8ea0b0819199b0d736f2397225","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw skills check","workdir":"/Users/palpet/.openclaw/workspace","yieldMs":10000},"partialJson":"{\"command\":\"openclaw skills check\",\"workdir\":\"/Users/palpet/.openclaw/workspace\",\"yieldMs\":10000}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_QviP0btSw1Tkfphci7BKVxYG|fc_070d3cbb0915198e0169c25b8ea0e88191814627b46cae6178","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 --version && which python3 && which pip3 || true && node --version && npm --version","workdir":"/Users/palpet/.openclaw/workspace","yieldMs":10000},"partialJson":"{\"command\":\"python3 --version && which python3 && which pip3 || true && node --version && npm --version\",\"workdir\":\"/Users/palpet/.openclaw/workspace\",\"yieldMs\":10000}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":140,"output":201,"cacheRead":41856,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":42197,"cost":{"input":0.00035000000000000005,"output":0.003015,"cacheRead":0.010464,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.013829}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774345097143,"responseId":"resp_070d3cbb0915198e0169c25b89a2f081919a7604e54c287a5f"}}
{"type":"message","id":"769846f8","parentId":"c3c0f857","timestamp":"2026-03-24T09:38:22.826Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_PFBZI6Gmo5npZSnpApa1EljP|fc_070d3cbb0915198e0169c25b8ea080819190c0037e7e4dbf5a","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Jimeng Auto Image Generator Skill\n\n## Description\n自动从xlsx文件读取分镜脚本，在即梦AI批量生成图片的自动化工具。\n\n## Features\n- 上传xlsx分镜脚本文件\n- 自动提取分镜提示词\n- 批量在即梦AI生成图片\n- 支持图片4.6模型、2K分辨率、16:9比例\n- 每个提示词生成3次\n- 进度显示\n\n## Requirements\n- Python 3.10+\n- openpyxl\n- Flask\n- Chrome浏览器 + OpenClaw浏览器扩展\n\n## Setup\n```bash\npip install openpyxl flask\n```\n\n## Usage\n1. 启动服务: `python app.py`\n2. 打开浏览器访问: http://localhost:5000\n3. 上传xlsx分镜脚本\n4. 点击开始生成\n\n## File Format\nxlsx文件需要包含以下列：\n- 镜号 (镜头编号)\n- 画面文字描述 (生成提示词)\n\n## Triggers\n- \"自动生图\"\n- \"批量生图\"\n- \"上传xlsx生图\"\n- \"jimeng\"\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774345102825}}
