{"type":"message","id":"107eed07","parentId":"ec705c92","timestamp":"2026-03-24T09:39:12.076Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_vzcCeERclZsHdGLCvkizrAuL|fc_070d3cbb0915198e0169c25bbe6c648191b616a5786fe1ae25","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Skills (15/61 ready)\n┌───────────┬────────────────────────────────┬────────────────────────────────────────────────────┬────────────────────┐\n│ Status    │ Skill                          │ Description                                        │ Source             │\n├───────────┼────────────────────────────────┼────────────────────────────────────────────────────┼────────────────────┤\n│ ✓ ready   │ 📦 feishu-doc                  │ Feishu document read/write operations. Activate    │ openclaw-extra     │\n│           │                                │ when user mentions Feishu docs, cloud docs, or     │                    │\n│           │                                │ docx links.                                        │                    │\n│ ✓ ready   │ 📦 feishu-drive                │ Feishu cloud storage file management. Activate     │ openclaw-extra     │\n│           │                                │ when user mentions cloud space, folders, drive.    │                    │\n│ ✓ ready   │ 📦 feishu-perm                 │ Feishu permission management for documents and     │ openclaw-extra     │\n│           │                                │ files. Activate when user mentions sharing,        │                    │\n│           │                                │ permissions, collaborators.                        │                    │\n│ ✓ ready   │ 📦 feishu-wiki                 │ Feishu knowledge base navigation. Activate when    │ openclaw-extra     │\n│           │                                │ user mentions knowledge base, wiki, or wiki links. │                    │\n│ ✗ missing │ 🔐 1password                   │ Set up and use 1Password CLI (op). Use when        │ openclaw-bundled   │