{"type":"message","id":"26d192c2","parentId":"7201e4ab","timestamp":"2026-03-24T09:40:29.904Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"我已经验证出两个硬问题：\n\n1. **SearXNG 没启动**  \n   `localhost:8080` 连不上，所以 `news-aggregator` / `searxng_search` 现在只是“被识别”，还不能真搜。\n\n2. **jimeng-auto-generator 代码和当前环境不匹配**  \n   它依赖 `flask + openpyxl`，而你机器当前缺这俩包；另外它脚本里有些浏览器 CLI 用法也像是旧版写法，后面还得再修。\n\n我先继续把 skill 本身做成更稳一点：最起码补一版依赖/启动说明，并检查 `app.py` 能否在不联网安装依赖前先做语法层面体检。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_070d3cbb0915198e0169c25c07962881918364cf278f818bc3\",\"phase\":\"commentary\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_RKjeKq1871fhMQRsF1npCnpE|fc_070d3cbb0915198e0169c25c0dcc208191a741b68ddbfaf5ec","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 -m py_compile /Users/palpet/.openclaw/workspace/skills/jimeng-auto-generator/app.py /Users/palpet/.openclaw/workspace/skills/jimeng-auto-generator/auto_submit.py","workdir":"/Users/palpet/.openclaw/workspace","yieldMs":10000},"partialJson":"{\"command\":\"python3 -m py_compile /Users/palpet/.openclaw/workspace/skills/jimeng-auto-generator/app.py /Users/palpet/.openclaw/workspace/skills/jimeng-auto-generator/auto_submit.py\",\"workdir\":\"/Users/palpet/.openclaw/workspace\",\"yieldMs\":10000}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_gULVtkXRjtO5PPEEbqvvTLWg|fc_070d3cbb0915198e0169c25c0dcc4481918a0f876a185d9869","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"sed -n '220,520p' /Users/palpet/.openclaw/workspace/skills/jimeng-auto-generator/app.py","workdir":"/Users/palpet/.openclaw/workspace","yieldMs":10000},"partialJson":"{\"command\":\"sed -n '220,520p' /Users/palpet/.openclaw/workspace/skills/jimeng-auto-generator/app.py\",\"workdir\":\"/Users/palpet/.openclaw/workspace\",\"yieldMs\":10000}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":2858,"output":343,"cacheRead":56576,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":59777,"cost":{"input":0.007145,"output":0.005145,"cacheRead":0.014143999999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0