feishu_drive: Registered feishu_drive tool\n[plugins] feishu_bitable: Registered bitable tools\n[info]: [ 'client ready' ]\n[plugins] feishu_doc: Registered feishu_doc, feishu_app_scopes\n[plugins] feishu_chat: Registered feishu_chat tool\n[plugins] feishu_wiki: Registered feishu_wiki tool\n[plugins] feishu_drive: Registered feishu_drive tool\n[plugins] feishu_bitable: Registered bitable tools\n[plugins] feishu_doc: Registered feishu_doc, feishu_app_scopes\n[plugins] feishu_chat: Registered feishu_chat tool\n[plugins] feishu_wiki: Registered feishu_wiki tool\n[plugins] feishu_drive: Registered feishu_drive tool\n[plugins] feishu_bitable: Registered bitable tools\n[plugins] feishu_doc: Registered feishu_doc, feishu_app_scopes\n[plugins] feishu_chat: Registered feishu_chat tool\n[plugins] feishu_wiki: Registered feishu_wiki tool\n[plugins] feishu_drive: Registered feishu_drive tool\n[plugins] feishu_bitable: Registered bitable tools\n[plugins] feishu_doc: Registered feishu_doc, feishu_app_scopes\n[plugins] feishu_chat: Registered feishu_chat tool\n[plugins] feishu_wiki: Registered feishu_wiki tool\n[plugins] feishu_drive: Registered feishu_drive tool\n[plugins] feishu_bitable: Registered bitable tools\n✅ Sent via Feishu. Message ID: om_x100b5311bcf8a4bcb36ecf7e2a14d0e","cwd":"/Users/palpet/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774346019787}}
{"type":"message","id":"9f8d295e","parentId":"cfa4c17c","timestamp":"2026-03-24T09:53:49.245Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 修好了，问题不在飞书本身，在于我刚才调用方式错了。\n\n我已经实际打通并发出去了一条测试消息，说明：\n\n- **飞书主动发消息可用**\n- 正确通道就是 `feishu`\n- 可以直接按你的飞书用户 ID 发\n\n刚才我已经成功发出一条测试消息给你。  \n所以后面如果我要主动 ping 你，不会再像刚才那样没反应了。\n\n顺手也确认了一下你前面关心的点：\n\n- **Codex 用量状态能看到**\n  - 5小时：**84% left**\n  - 周：**96% left**\n\n所以你刚才说“如果太费就切 5.4 nano”这件事，我会照着做，但目前看还没到特别危险的程度。\n\n接下来我继续按你说的两条线一起推进：\n\n1. 修 **即梦自动提交**\n2. 修 **本地搜索 / SearXNG**\n\n修到下一版能交差，我就直接：\n- 在这里回你\n- 同时也可以主动飞书 ping 你一下","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_070d3cbb0915198e0169c25f25d3e08191bdfaca748efe6f0c\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":765,"output":257,"cacheRead":73728,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":74750,"cost":{"input":0.0019125000000000001,"output":0.003855,"cacheRead":0.018432,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0241995}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774346019789,"responseId":"resp_070d3cbb0915198e0169c25f24e6b88191aa1a0f9b73b34e04"}}
