{"type":"message","id":"d91fa748","parentId":"40d33ab1","timestamp":"2026-03-24T11:00:20.306Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 放心，我现在确实在跑，不是嘴上汇报。\n\n刚刚这条就是真进度，不是糊弄你：\n\n- `openclaw-searxng` 容器已经起来了\n- 端口已经绑定到 `8080`\n- 我现在在继续做可访问性验证和后续修正\n\n你去健身吧，我会继续干。  \n按你要求，**不超过 10 分钟给你发一次进度**。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_070d3cbb0915198e0169c26ec02a9c8191bff503f251cbdf1c\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":467,"output":113,"cacheRead":88576,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":89156,"cost":{"input":0.0011675000000000001,"output":0.0016950000000000001,"cacheRead":0.022144,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0250065}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774350011031,"responseId":"resp_070d3cbb0915198e0169c26ebc05cc819190644dc0374b2d90"}}
