{"type":"message","id":"931179fb","parentId":"4cef45b8","timestamp":"2026-03-24T11:13:57.545Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 我已经单开了一个 subagent，专门做这件事：\n\n- 目标：给你设计一套 **OpenClaw 稳定性 + 掉线自愈 + 远程修复** 方案\n- 会重点考虑：\n  - 本机自动检测\n  - 挂了自动重启\n  - 飞书/消息告警\n  - 你那台腾讯云服务器怎么接进来做远程修复\n  - 哪些能自动修，哪些必须人工介入\n\n我这边主线还继续修即梦和 SearXNG。  \n等这个 subagent 出结果，我也一并汇报给你。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_070d3cbb0915198e0169c271f295288191bcdd794f64d42981\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":270,"output":154,"cacheRead":93824,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":94248,"cost":{"input":0.000675,"output":0.00231,"cacheRead":0.023455999999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.026441}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774350831262,"responseId":"resp_070d3cbb0915198e0169c271f017d4819184b437321803044c"}}
{"type":"message","id":"b8d1ab72","parentId":"931179fb","timestamp":"2026-03-24T11:13:57.781Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b531342f580b4c4ea38411b08694\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_2369d90c137e41169ecf225ba3a7e356\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_2369d90c137e41169ecf225ba3a7e356\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-03-24 19:09 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_2369d90c137e41169ecf225ba3a7e356\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_2369d90c137e41169ecf225ba3a7e356\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_2369d90c137e41169ecf225ba3a7e356\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b531342f580b4c4ea38411b08694]\nou_2369d90c137e41169ecf225ba3a7e356: 现在还有一个事儿，需要你去做，是关于openclaw稳定性的事儿。你可以新建一个subagnet去做。就是我以前的mac mini就是经常gateway不稳定，然后不知道啥情况就掉了。由于这个是公司用的openclaw 所以需要一个非常稳定的方案。让这个openclaw可以自己长期的跑起来，然后我这边还有一个腾讯云服务器上的openclaw可以作为你的ai运维，让你挂掉的时候可以做修复，这个是我的方案，你有什么方案，按照马斯克的第一性原则来思考问题"}],"timestamp":1774350837776}}
