{"type":"message","id":"31b64e75","parentId":"47ede0fa","timestamp":"2026-03-24T11:48:06.336Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 嗯，这个“硬规则”模式对我也好。\n\n因为这样就很清楚了：\n\n- 什么是必须做的\n- 什么不能漏\n- 什么该主动汇报\n- 什么卡住了该直接来问你\n\n以后我会尽量把这种关键规则都当成**执行约束**，不是当成“可能记得的提醒”。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_070d3cbb0915198e0169c279f422408191bb7c9e4b99e0301f\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":377,"output":90,"cacheRead":166656,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":167123,"cost":{"input":0.0009425000000000001,"output":0.00135,"cacheRead":0.041664,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0439565}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774352880916,"responseId":"resp_070d3cbb0915198e0169c279f26ff48191966a40e24e14b8e7"}}
