{"type":"message","id":"cfc892ad","parentId":"9a9ad793","timestamp":"2026-03-24T11:50:01.165Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 对，**不本质影响**我继续做这三件事：\n\n1. 即梦自动化\n2. SearXNG\n3. watchdog\n\n你现在这样聊天，更多是：\n\n- 会稍微打断我节奏\n- 但不会让我没法继续做\n\n所以只要你**别去动我正在测的页面本身**，我这边主线还是能继续推进的。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_070d3cbb0915198e0169c27a6726448191abf2aea54594cdf9\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":706,"output":99,"cacheRead":168192,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":168997,"cost":{"input":0.001765,"output":0.001485,"cacheRead":0.042047999999999995,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.045298}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774352996455,"responseId":"resp_070d3cbb0915198e0169c27a65dd0c8191a005504f1b40788e"}}
