{"type":"message","id":"018e19d8","parentId":"9dd7a5b0","timestamp":"2026-03-24T12:16:45.478Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 收到，那腾讯云这条我先不展开。\n\n## 现在确定下来的策略\n- **即梦：方案 A（稳一点）**\n- **SearXNG：方案 A（本地优先）**\n- **watchdog：方案 B（自动重启一次）**\n- **腾讯云远程运维：先搁置**\n\n这样挺好，范围一下收紧了。  \n我现在就按这三条已拍板的策略继续推进。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_070d3cbb0915198e0169c280ab48808191b07862f4b94b85d5\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":409,"output":111,"cacheRead":174720,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":175240,"cost":{"input":0.0010225000000000002,"output":0.001665,"cacheRead":0.04368,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0463675}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774354601506,"responseId":"resp_070d3cbb0915198e0169c280aa43108191b740eec7c19527c4"}}
