{"type":"message","id":"23b3451b","parentId":"bdff97ef","timestamp":"2026-03-24T13:42:26.785Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have all the information I need to design the watchdog. Let me now write the watchdog script. The plan is:\n\n1. A bash script that runs via `openclaw cron` periodically\n2. Uses `openclaw health --json` as the probe\n3. Fails once → wait 30-60s → retry\n4. Fails twice → `openclaw gateway restart`\n5. After restart, probe again → if still bad → alert (告警) and stop\n\nLet me write the actual script now.","thinkingSignature":"cef774077b51748214fb06be2b8fe3bb162d2531119eecda22e2eff7ad03e7c2"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_u0iltogx8jek_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"#!/bin/bash\n# watchdog_openclaw.sh\n# OpenClaw 本地 watchdog - 方案B：自动重启一次\n# 策略：fail一次→重试→fail两次→restart→检查→还不行则停\n\nset -e\n\nLOG=\"/tmp/openclaw-watchdog.log\"\nSTATE_DIR=\"/tmp/openclaw-watchdog\"\nmkdir -p \"$STATE_DIR\"\n\n# 探针命令：用 openclaw health --json 检查网关状态\ncheck_gateway() {\n    openclaw health --json 2>/dev/null | python3.11 -c \"\nimport sys, json\nd = json.load(sys.stdin)\nok = d.get('ok', False)\ngateway = d.get('gateway', {})\nrpc_ok = gateway.get('rpc', {}).get('ok', False) if isinstance(gateway, dict) else False\nprint('1' if (ok and rpc_ok) else '0')\n\" 2>/dev/null || echo \"0\"\n}\n\nlog() {\n    echo \"$(date '+%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S') [WATCHDOG] $1\" >> \"$LOG\"\n}\n\n# 主逻辑\nfail_count_file=\"$STATE_DIR/fail_count\"\nlast_restart_file=\"$STATE_DIR/last_restart\"\nalerted_file=\"$STATE_DIR/alerted\"\n\n# 读取失败计数\nFAIL_COUNT=$(cat \"$fail_count_file\" 2>/dev/null || echo \"0\")\nLAST_RESTART=$(cat \"$last_restart_file\" 2>/dev/null || echo \"0\")\nNOW=$(date +%s)\n\nlog \"=== Start check === fail_count=$FAIL_COUNT\"\n\n# 执行探针\nRESULT=$(check_gateway)\nlog \"Probe result: $RESULT\"\n\nif [ \"$RESULT\" = \"1\" ]; then\n    # 健康：重置失败计数\n    echo \"0\" > \"$fail_count_file\"\n    log \"Gateway OK - reset fail count\"\n    exit 0\nfi\n\n# 不健康\nFAIL_COUNT=$((FAIL_COUNT + 1))\necho \"$FAIL_COUNT\" > \"$fail_count_file\"\n\nif [ \"$FAIL_COUNT\" -eq 1 ]; then\n    # 第一次失败：等待30秒后重试\n    log \"First failure - waiting 30s then retry...\"\n    sleep 30\n    RESULT=$(check_gateway)\n    if [ \"$RESULT\" = \"1\" ]; then\n        echo \"0\" > \"$fail_count_file\"\n        log \"Retry OK - recovered\"\n        exit 0\n    else\n        FAIL_COUNT=2\n        echo \"2\" > \"$fail_count_file\"\n    fi\nfi\n\nif [ \"$FAIL_COUNT\" -ge 2 ]; then\n    # 第二次失败：执行重启\n    log \"Second failure - executing restart...\"\n    openclaw gateway restart 2>&1 | tee -a \"$LOG\"\n    echo \"$NOW\" > \"$last_restart_file\"\n    \n    # 等待重启生效\n    sleep 15\n    \n    # 检查重启后状态\n    RESULT=$(check_gateway)\n    if [ \"$RESULT\" = \"1\" ]; then\n        echo \"0\" > \"$fail_count_file\"\n        log \"Restart succeeded - recovered\"\n        exit 0\n    else\n        # 重启后仍不健康，告警并停止\n        log \"Restart failed - alerting and giving up\"\n        \n        # 发送飞书告警\n        openclaw message send --channel feishu --target ou_2369d90c137e41169ecf225ba3a7e356 \\\n            --message \"⚠️ OpenClaw Watchdog: 重启后仍不健康，已停止自动修复。请人工检查 Mac mini 上的 OpenClaw 服务状态。\" 2>&1 | tee -a \"$LOG\"\n        \n        # 标记已告警，不再继续重启\n        touch \"$alerted_file\"\n        exit 1\n    fi\nfi\n","file_path":"/Users/palpet/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/watchdog_openclaw.sh"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":39823,"output":966,"cacheRead":16722,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":57511,"cost":{"input":0.0119469,"output":0.0011592,"cacheRead":0.0010033199999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.01410942}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774359723218,"responseId":"0611c7ab82d9c34e87c5b45ac00cb457"}}
