{"type":"message","id":"617dc61f","parentId":"070d55ea","timestamp":"2026-03-24T13:55:16.347Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The message was sent successfully with ID `om_x100b531d35a0f8b0b35bbd58910f045`. The ID `ou_2369d90c137e41169ecf225ba3a7e356` works fine for sending. The earlier failure might have been a transient error.\n\nNow I should also report the other two decisions the watchdog raised:\n1. OpenAI Codex rate limit - suggest switching primary model to MiniMax-M2.7\n2. Security audit criticals - groupPolicy=\"open\"\n\nThe user still hasn't explicitly responded to those. Let me also update the watchdog executor with the correct target ID.\n\n\nI'll summarize what we've accomplished so far: the watchdog is operational with regular checks, the alert system is functioning with the correct ID, but there are still two pending decisions around the model selection and security policy that need user approval.","thinkingSignature":"d0696daef6be0555153b63320d1929c7c26ff75bf6cf894700784be2c6f35cc5"},{"type":"text","text":"**发送成功 ✅** ID: `om_x100b531d35a0f8b0b35bbd58910f045`\n\n`ou_2369d90c137e41169ecf225ba3a7e356` 这个 ID 是通的，之前那个报错应该是偶发网络抖动。\n\nwatchdog 告警会继续用这个 ID。\n\n---\n\n另外还有两件事等你拍板：\n\n**1. 模型策略** — 建议把 MiniMax-M2.7 改为主力，减少 Codex rate limit 影响。同意吗？\n\n**2. 安全审计 Critical × 3** — Feishu `groupPolicy=\"open\"` 风险，建议改成 `allowlist`。要改吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":48759,"output":332,"cacheRead":18850,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":67941,"cost":{"input":0.014627699999999999,"output":0.0003984,"cacheRead":0.0011309999999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.016157099999999997}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774360503138,"responseId":"0611cab73949f0451ee82bc28ebf8273"}}
