{"type":"message","id":"bc7da45f","parentId":"e25b9f3d","timestamp":"2026-03-24T14:28:14.053Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to check Feishu and reply to their messages there. Let me use the feishu tools to check messages. But wait - looking at the tools available, I don't have a \"read_messages\" or \"get_messages\" tool for Feishu. I have feishu_chat but that's for chat operations (members, info, member_info), not reading messages.\n\nLet me think about this. The user is saying \"现在看看飞书，回一下我消息\" - check Feishu and reply to their messages. \n\nLooking at the available Feishu tools:\n- feishu_chat: members, info, member_info\n\n\n- feishu_doc: read/write documents\n- feishu_wiki: knowledge base\n- feishu_drive: cloud storage\n- feishu_bitable: tables\n- feishu_app_scopes: permissions\n\nNone of these tools can actually retrieve and read messages from Feishu conversations. The feishu message sending works through OpenClaw's message tool with the --channel feishu flag, but there's no corresponding way to fetch or read incoming Feishu messages with the available tools.\n\nI should be straightforward with the user that I don't have the capability to read their Feishu messages, even though I can send outbound messages to them.","thinkingSignature":"6a7906acfc42e581f13c336a7c4f642c40925740ee81470e8e6dca5f7991cf96"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 我查了一下，能发飞书消息，但**没有办法主动读取飞书聊天记录**——我现有的飞书工具只支持发消息、查文档、看知识库，没有读消息的权限。\n\n也就是说：\n\n- **能发**：能通过 OpenClaw 给你发飞书消息 ✅\n- **能读**：没有这个能力 ❌\n\n---\n\n如果你想让我回你飞书里的消息，需要：\n\n1. **你把那条消息截图/复制发给我**，我就能帮你回复\n2. 或者**给 OpenClaw 的飞书机器人开消息读取权限**\n\n你看看哪种方式方便？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":99,"output":406,"cacheRead":66936,"cacheWrite":143,"totalTokens":67584,"cost":{"input":0.0000297,"output":0.00048719999999999997,"cacheRead":0.0040161599999999995,"cacheWrite":0.000053625,"total":0.004586684999999999}},"stopReason":