{"type":"message","id":"14dc7398","parentId":"01b4133f","timestamp":"2026-03-24T14:29:09.080Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Looking at the Feishu app scopes, I can see that the app already has `im:message:readonly` permission which is the \"Read messages\" permission. So the permission itself is already granted.\n\nThe issue is that OpenClaw's toolset just doesn't expose a \"read messages\" tool - it's not a permission problem. Looking at the available tools, there's no `feishu_message_read` or similar.\n\nSo the permissions are there, but OpenClaw doesn't currently have a tool to use that permission for reading messages. This is an OpenClaw capability limitation, not a Feishu app permission issue.\n\nI should tell the user that:\n1. The permission `im:message:readonly` is already granted in Feishu\n\n\n2. But OpenClaw's current implementation doesn't expose a message reading tool - the toolset is limited\n3. If they want this capability, they might need to either request it as a feature from OpenClaw or explore a custom API integration","thinkingSignature":"4ec49af4832735f336742dbd3bb055810d51e6fe72696c09835c69b18a94ad84"},{"type":"text","text":"权限其实已经有了——`im:message:readonly`（读消息）已经在飞书侧授权了。\n\n但问题是：**OpenClaw 目前的工具集里没有\"读取消息\"这个功能**，不是权限问题，是工具本身就没开放。\n\n也就是说：\n\n- 飞书已经把读消息权限给我了 ✅\n- 但 OpenClaw 没有提供调用这个权限的工具 ❌\n\n---\n\n这是一个产品能力限制，不是配置问题。\n\n如果想让我真正读取飞书消息，需要 OpenClaw 开放对应的 `message read` 工具，或者通过飞书开放 API 直接对接。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":49864,"output":326,"cacheRead":18850,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":69040,"cost":{"input":0.014959199999999999,"output":0.00039119999999999997,"cacheRead":0.0011309999999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.016481399999999997}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774362531648,"responseId":"0611d2a5d25606ba5fcf05a6d1ee4943"}}
