{"type":"message","id":"c9b9d232","parentId":"a438354d","timestamp":"2026-03-24T15:10:15.180Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b531edb8074a0c375e4f517096c0\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_2369d90c137e41169ecf225ba3a7e356\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_2369d90c137e41169ecf225ba3a7e356\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-03-24 23:10 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_2369d90c137e41169ecf225ba3a7e356\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_2369d90c137e41169ecf225ba3a7e356\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_2369d90c137e41169ecf225ba3a7e356\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b531edb8074a0c375e4f517096c0]\nou_2369d90c137e41169ecf225ba3a7e356: 现在每天晚上3点钟把skill还有一些就是跟你相关的东西都备份到Github上面吧。Github不用做覆盖，就按照每个日期去迭代就行了。然后只保留一周的数据，不用太多。以前的就可以删掉"}],"timestamp":1774365015176}}
{"type":"message","id":"9dc685f7","parentId":"c9b9d232","timestamp":"2026-03-24T15:10:29.562Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 可以做，但这里有两个边界我先说清：\n\n1. **备份到 GitHub** 属于外部写入  \n2. **删除旧备份** 也是有状态变更\n\n所以我建议我先把方案定成可执行的，再由你确认一次 GitHub 仓库目标。\n\n## 我理解你的需求\n每天 **凌晨 3 点** 自动做一次备份，内容包括：\n\n- `skills/`\n- 跟我相关的关键文件/目录\n  - 比如：`AGENTS.md`\n  - `SOUL.md`\n  - `USER.md`\n  - `TOOLS.md`\n  - `IDENTITY.md`\n  - `memory/`\n  - 可能还有 `HEARTBEAT.md`\n- 备份到 **GitHub**\n- **不覆盖历史**\n- 以**日期迭代**\n- **只保留 7 天**\n- 更早的自动删掉\n\n## 我建议的实现方式\n### 方案\n- 本地准备一个专门的 backup 目录或 backup repo\n- 每天 03:00：\n  1. 把当天快照复制进去，目录名按日期\n  2. commit\n  3. push 到 GitHub\n  4. 清理 7 天前的备份目录\n  5. 再 commit + push 一次清理结果\n\n### 日期结构\n例如：\n- `backups/2026-03-24/`\n- `backups/2026-03-25/`\n\n这样就不会覆盖。\n\n## 我需要你补一个关键值\n### GitHub 仓库\n你要我推到哪个仓库？\n\n给我任一一种都行：\n- 仓库地址\n- `owner/repo`\n- 或者告诉我“新建一个 repo，名字你定”\n\n## 我默认会备份这些\n如果你不特别改，我会默认备份：\n\n- `/Users/palpet/.openclaw/workspace/skills/`\n- `/Users/palpet/.openclaw/workspace/AGENTS.md`\n- `/Users/palpet/.openclaw/workspace/SOUL.md`\n- `/Users/palpet/.openclaw/workspace/USER.md`\n- `/Users/palpet/.openclaw/workspace/TOOLS.md`\n- `/Users/palpet/.openclaw/workspace/IDENTITY.md`\n- `/Users/palpet/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md`\n- `/Users/palpet/.openclaw/workspace/memory/`\n\n## 一句话\n这事可以做，而且适合做成 **cron + git 自动备份**。  \n你只要给我 **GitHub 仓库目标**，我就能继续往下落。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_070d3cbb0915198e0169c2a95a85a481918c809a558e3d8cea\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":469,"output":607,"cacheRead":71424,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":72500,"cost":{"input":0.0011725000000000001,"output":0.009105,"cacheRead":0.017856,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0281335}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774365015188,"responseId":"resp_070d3cbb0915198e0169c2a957e9e081918a51ea1497db0194"}}
