{"type":"message","id":"90493acc","parentId":"603fa675","timestamp":"2026-03-24T15:15:54.378Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Need answer maybe cannot know \"most popular\" from search alone; mention likely from ClawHub usage signals but no public ranking found. Maybe fetch docs?","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_070d3cbb0915198e0169c2aaa487108191b0dc954989d5a004\",\"phase\":\"commentary\"}"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 我刚搜了一下，**没找到一个官方公开的“最火 skill 排行榜”页面**。\n\n目前能确认的是：\n\n- **ClawHub** 确实是 OpenClaw 的官方/公开 skill registry\n- 文档里提到它有 **search、tags、usage signals**\n- 但我这轮公开搜索里，**没看到直接公开展示“当前最火 skill”榜单**\n\n## 所以更准确的回答是\n> **现在公开网页上，我还不能严谨地告诉你“最火的是哪一个 skill”。**\n\n如果你要，我接下来可以继续做两种测试：\n\n1. **继续深挖 ClawHub / docs / GitHub**\n   - 看有没有隐藏的 trending / popular 页面\n2. **给你一个“现在最值得装/最常被提到”的 skill 列表**\n   - 这个我可以基于公开资料给你一个实用版答案\n\n如果你愿意，我下一步就继续深挖一层，专门找 **“最火 / 最常用 / trending”** 的真实来源。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_070d3cbb0915198e0169c2aaa538fc8191881f1194074ec855\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":2357,"output":285,"cacheRead":74368,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":77010,"cost":{"input":0.0058925,"output":0.004275,"cacheRead":0.018592,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0287595}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774365340209,"responseId":"resp_070d3cbb0915198e0169c2aa9d5ed88191a0f2fa90b30520b4"}}
{"type":"message","id":"abe96656","parentId":"90493acc","timestamp":"2026-03-24T15:16:28.275Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b531ee259c8a0b3b68c11c320923\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_2369d90c137e41169ecf225ba3a7e356\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_2369d90c137e41169ecf225ba3a7e356\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-03-24 23:16 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_2369d90c137e41169ecf225ba3a7e356\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_2369d90c137e41169ecf225ba3a7e356\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_2369d90c137e41169ecf225ba3a7e356\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b531ee259c8a0b3b68c11c320923]\nou_2369d90c137e41169ecf225ba3a7e356: 给我一个最值得装的呗"}],"timestamp":1774365388271}}
{"type":"message","id":"d19bf893","parentId":"abe96656","timestamp":"2026-03-24T15:16:41.745Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 如果只让我给你 **一个最值得装的**，我会给：\n\n# **weather**\n\n## 为什么是它\n因为它几乎满足“好 skill”的几个核心条件：\n\n- **立刻有用**\n- **低风险**\n- **零账号门槛**\n- **不太会坏**\n- **调用频率高**\n- **返回结果容易验证**\n\n而且它不是那种“看起来很酷，但实际要折腾半天环境”的 skill。  \n装上之后基本就能直接用：\n\n- 今天几度\n- 明天会不会下雨\n- 未来几天走势\n\n这种需求非常高频。\n\n## 为什么不是别的\n如果按“一个 skill 最值得装”而不是“最炫”来选：\n\n- 不是最复杂的那个\n- 不是最依赖外部配置的那个\n- 不是最容易脆掉的那个\n\n而是：\n\n> **安装成本低、稳定性高、收益立刻可见。**\n\nweather 就非常符合。\n\n## 如果按你的使用场景再说一句\n你现在更适合的是：\n\n- **先装那些稳定、低维护、马上见效的**\n- 不是先追那些“自动化很猛但特别脆”的 skill\n\n所以如果只推荐一个，我推荐：\n\n> **weather**\n\n如果你愿意，我下一条可以直接给你：\n- **“最值得装的前 5 个”**  \n而不是只给 1 个。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_070d3cbb0915198e0169c2aad21f208191b27b433630b16f21\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":349,"output":325,"cacheRead":76928,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":77602,"cost":{"input":0.0008725000000000001,"output":0.004875,"cacheRead":0.019232,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.024979499999999998}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774365388282,"responseId":"resp_070d3cbb0915198e0169c2aacd57a48191a0a7aba41707e3d6"}}
