{"type":"message","id":"9415890c","parentId":"e9c9400f","timestamp":"2026-03-24T15:28:34.618Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 好，我记住了。\n\n## 以后模型切换策略就按这个来\n### 降级时\n- 如果 **GPT-5.4 / Codex** 限速或异常\n- 自动切到 **MiniMax-M2.7**\n\n### 恢复后\n- **不自动切回**\n- 我会先问你：\n\n> 要不要切回 GPT-5.4？\n\n因为你已经明确说了：\n\n- **GPT-5.4 成本更高**\n- 所以切回要先经过你确认\n\n这个策略我后面就按默认规则执行。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_070d3cbb0915198e0169c2ad9f9624819186b9178595022a54\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":118,"output":135,"cacheRead":85888,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":86141,"cost":{"input":0.000295,"output":0.002025,"cacheRead":0.021471999999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.023791999999999997}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774366107271,"responseId":"resp_070d3cbb0915198e0169c2ad9e451081918c24cb3976c2c08b"}}
