{"type":"message","id":"cb3d0aeb","parentId":"bc86d10d","timestamp":"2026-03-24T15:59:09.316Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b531f027c20a8c49beff209d6800\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_2369d90c137e41169ecf225ba3a7e356\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_2369d90c137e41169ecf225ba3a7e356\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-03-24 23:59 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_2369d90c137e41169ecf225ba3a7e356\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_2369d90c137e41169ecf225ba3a7e356\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_2369d90c137e41169ecf225ba3a7e356\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b531f027c20a8c49beff209d6800]\nou_2369d90c137e41169ecf225ba3a7e356: @Watchdog 检查结果：当前正常。\nOpenClaw gateway 正在运行\n`openclaw gateway status` 显示 `RPC probe: ok`\n监听地址正常：`127.0.0.1:18789`\n最近几次 cron run 都是 `status=ok`\n补充：\n今晚 23:18 左右确实发生过一次“两次探测失败 → 自动重启”的异常\n但从后续多次 run 记录看，自动重启后已经恢复，之后检查连续正常\n`/tmp/openclaw-watchdog.log` 仍停在 `Second failure - executing restart...`，说明日志收尾还不完整，不过不影响当前健康状态\n`HEARTBEAT.md` 还是空模板，没有额外巡检任务\n结论：\n本次无需告警；系统目前健康。唯一待改进点是把 watchdog 重启后的“复检成功/最终结论”补进日志。    为啥这个又弹出来了？"}],"timestamp":1774367949310}}
{"type":"message","id":"d0c6ca6c","parentId":"cb3d0aeb","timestamp":"2026-03-24T15:59:23.774Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking why the watchdog notification appeared again. The watchdog cron job seems to be sending notifications even though the user said to stay silent during healthy hours. This is because the watchdog cron is set to \"announce\" mode, which sends results to the chat.\n\nThe issue is that the watchdog cron job has delivery mode set to \"announce\" - it announces the result of each run. Even though the system is healthy, it's still sending these \"检查结果：当前正常\" messages to the chat.\n\nThe user wants silence during nighttime unless there's an actual problem. This is the cron job's \"announce\" feature causing健康 notifications to be pushed to the chat.\n\nI should explain why this is happening and offer to either:\n1. Disable the announce mode for the watchdog cron job\n\n\n2. Configure it to only announce on failures instead of every run\n\nLet me check the watchdog cron job configuration - it was created with `--announce` which means it will announce every time it runs, even when healthy. The fix is to disable announce or change to \"no-deliver\" mode.","thinkingSignature":"2341ce270857a8ea135eb5578454abdc345352f9d0e230b0ba5537634c3ab048"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 因为 watchdog cron 当时建的时候设了 `--announce`（结果播报），所以每次跑完都会往这里发一条，不管健康还是异常。\n\n这就导致了：\n- 夜里健康也弹\n- 用户说“别发了”但还在发\n\n**解决方式**：把 watchdog 的 announce 关掉，改为只在异常时告警。\n\n现在关掉：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_7sb4pgqmkwar_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw cron edit 7dd53373-8af4-462b-81c6-87c3805d82de --no-deliver 2>&1","timeout":10}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":80,"output":371,"cacheRead":83257,"cacheWrite":647,"totalTokens":84355,"cost":{"input":0.000024,"output":0.0004452,"cacheRead":0.0049954199999999995,"cacheWrite":0.000242625,"total":0.